CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 17, 1963, pg. 3 reads: "Concern - Shown above is Mrs. Daisy Curry, who is deeply concerned about the future of 7-month-old Terrence and her five other children. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Daisy Curry feeding bottle to seven month old Terrence and holding protest sign reading "Do your children live like this in Squirrel Hill?  We are still human not animals," in small bedroom
